digilib.io

Class ImageSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • digilib.io.ImageSet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImageFileSet

    public class ImageSet
extends Object
    Set of ImageInputs of the same image in different resolutions. The images are be added in the order of higher to lower resolutions. The first image is considered the hires "original".
    Author:
    casties
